522
00:30:49,722 --> 00:30:51,215
They're the best at what they do.

523
00:30:51,618 --> 00:30:53,845
They will find her
if she can be found.

524
00:30:54,262 --> 00:30:57,006
And, Van Pelt, snap out of it.
Wasn't your fault.

525
00:30:57,667 --> 00:30:58,368
Yes, ma'am, but--

526
00:30:58,488 --> 00:31:00,291
move on.

527
00:31:01,736 --> 00:31:04,145
All right. Where are we on
