532
00:31:15,161 --> 00:31:18,208
It's after a killer with Red
John connections. Any leads?

533
00:31:18,328 --> 00:31:20,679
Well, off photos he took,
we've id'd six possible locations

534
00:31:20,799 --> 00:31:22,642
