546
00:31:46,969 --> 00:31:48,336
Some rest? Oh, just...

547
00:31:48,337 --> 00:31:51,396
Lie down and catch up on some z's.

548
00:31:51,727 --> 00:31:53,628
<i>Kick back with a good book. Rest?</i>

549
00:31:54,964 --> 00:31:55,697
I'm fine.

550
