Debatable.

551
00:31:57,929 --> 00:32:00,468
Do you want me to ask the psych
counselor for an evaluation?

552
00:33:11,849 --> 00:33:13,849
Sorry.

553
00:33:36,672 --> 00:33:38,632
Leave a message.
I'll call you back.

554
00:33:38,962 --> 00:33:41,284
Lisbon, it's Jane. Uh, I found it.

555
00:33:41,404 --> 00:33:43,608
It's 52 north Esperanza.

556
00:33:44,046 --> 00:33:46,226
Hotel Del corona in Salinger Mill.

557
00:33:47,017 --> 00:33:48,252
Uh, I am gonna...

558
00:33:51,469 --> 00:33:53,304
Uh, I-I'm gonna wait for you

