00:33:53,424 --> 00:33:54,645
at, uh, Kenny's

560
00:33:55,292 --> 00:33:58,592
Okay? Give me a call when
you get this message.

561
00:33:58,712 --> 00:34:00,594
Thank you.

562
00:34:44,970 --> 00:34:46,336
Ha

563
